locked it from the outside?!

245
00:16:42,501 --> 00:16:45,751
Locking the door is no problem at all...

246
00:16:45,751 --> 00:16:48,531
if you use that projector, that is!

247
00:16:49,911 --> 00:16:51,531
Projector?

248
00:16:52,041 --> 00:16:56,251
W-What are you talking about?
How could a projector do that?

249
00:16:56,251 --> 00:17:00,251
Tadokoro-san,
I've figured it all out, you know...

250
00:17:00,251 --> 00:17:03,461
