270
00:18:08,791 --> 00:18:10,401
All done, Dad!

271
00:18:12,361 --> 00:18:14,621
Now everything is set.

272
00:18:14,621 --> 00:18:16,831
Ran. Start the projector.

273
00:18:16,831 --> 00:18:17,751
Right!

274
00:18:42,211 --> 00:18:45,981
This is how Tadokoro-san
locked the door.

275
00:18:45,981 --> 00:18:51,121
But, unfortunately for him,
as the film was being pulled in,

276
00:18:51,121 --> 00:18:56,201
