the curtain rail and remained there.

277
00:18:56,411 --> 00:19:02,161
On the piece of tape are small,
square marks... from perforations.

278
00:19:02,161 --> 00:19:05,881
The square holes in
the film, in other words.

279
00:19:06,161 --> 00:19:10,711
